'''Útför''' is the Icelandic word for funeral in full Icelandic letters.
<br> See English spelling [[Utfor]]

<li> In Iceland the funeral can be held from 5 to 14 days after the persons death.
<li> Before the funeral a [[kistulagning]] is held. It is a small funeral service or a [[wake (ceremony)]] held for the closest familymembers and friends. It takes up to 30 minutesa and is ususaly held in a small funeral chappel (kapella).